reviewText: I love Nicolas Cage and this set has all of my favorite movies of his.  It is a real treat.

Well not a bad collection. But It could happen to you is by far and away the best movie in this set. Absolutely love this movie Nicholas Cage and Bridgette Fonda are brilliant in this film and it's up there with my all time favourite films. Buy this movie even if you don't buy this collection buy it by itself it's really good film.
ok
wanted "It Could Happen To You"... got 2 extras for free...
If you're a Nicholas Cage fan, this is a GREAT BUY!!!!  Each dvd comes in it's own jacket, unlike others that are tri-folds. Excellent video and audio quality!  A BEST BUY!!!
I love buying these movies, I got a lot of moves and im buying to replace a lot we lost in our moving

I was thrilled to find three Nicholas Cage movies for one low price, and they are the three I adore.  The seller was wonderful in making sure it was packaged securely and it arrived way ahead of what was promised.

Three pack was a bonus when searching for Peggy Sue Got Married movie.  The other two Nicolas Cage movies are enjoyalble. For those folks who didn't wish to study high school Algebra and haven't found any use for the subject, you will enjoy Peggy Sue's memorable reply to her Algebra teacher: "Well, Mr Snelgrove, I happen to know that in the future I will not have the slightest use for algebra, and I speak from experience."  Priceless!
We enjoy watching Nicholas Cage, and Shirley Maclaine is terrific as well.  The movie is a nice evening's entertainment and neither actor disappoints.
Agradables peliculas, La oferta tiene un muy buen precio por el hecho de ser un paquete de las 3 peliculas
